Class ForwardUndoCompositeOperation

    ICompositeOperation, IUndoableOperation, ITransactionalOperation

    public class ForwardUndoCompositeOperation
extends AbstractCompositeOperation
    The ForwardUndoCompositeOperation is an AbstractCompositeOperation which undoes its combined operations in the same order as they are executed.
